CustomField.description: API name of the custom field on the Expense object that is used to determine the monthly time period any Deliverable expense is added to. This enables you to control the month in which expenses are placed.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: API name of the custom field on the Expense object that is used to determine the monthly time period any Deliverable expense revenue is added to. This enables you to control the month in which the revenue is placed.
CustomField.label: Custom Date for Deliverable Expenses
